Ini sungguh tidak menyenangkan.

52
00:04:40,067 --> 00:04:41,967
Taejoo!

53
00:04:41,967 --> 00:04:44,100
Itu hanya lelucon, hanya lelucon.

54
00:04:49,536 --> 00:04:51,100
- Dasar brengsek!
- Hei, hei!

55
00:04:51,100 --> 00:04:53,300
Tunggu, tunggu!

56
00:05:01,267 --> 00:05:03,967
Apakah kamu takut? Takut kamu tertembak?

57
00:05:03,967 --> 00:05:05,033
Dasar brengsek!

58
